---

<section class="hero" aria-label="Introduction">
  <div class="hero-bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <div class="grid-lines"></div>
    <div class="glow glow-1"></div>
    <div class="glow glow-2"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container hero-inner">
    <p class="eyebrow reveal">Kurt Kluth · SQL Server Architect · San Clemente, CA</p>

    <h1 class="h-display reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 0.08s">
      Some engineers work <em class="serif-accent">near</em> the database.<br />
      I work <em class="serif-accent">inside</em> it.
    </h1>

    <p class="lede reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 0.16s">
      Twenty-five years inside the SQL Server engine, from the raw, dangerous era of
      extended stored procedures to modern CLR-based in-engine services. I build governed
      extensibility, hardened execution boundaries, and cross-platform logic that your
      team can still maintain a decade from now.
    </p>

    <div class="hero-cta reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 0.24s">
      <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#work">
        See the work
        <svg width="15" height="15" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M5 12h14m-6-6 6 6-6 6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="https://github.com/kurtkluth" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        github.com/kurtkluth
      </a>
    </div>

    <figure class="terminal reveal" style="--reveal-delay: 0.34s" aria-label="Example T-SQL: deploying a CLR assembly">
      <figcaption class="terminal-bar">
        <span class="dot" style="background:#ff5f57"></span>
        <span class="dot" style="background:#febc2e"></span>
        <span class="dot" style="background:#28c840"></span>
        <span class="terminal-title">sqlcmd (master)</span>
      </figcaption>
      <pre><code><span class="c">-- The old way died for good reasons. This is the new one.</span>
<span class="k">CREATE ASSEMBLY</span> [Sqlclr.Services]
<span class="k">FROM</span> <span class="s">'/opt/mssql/assemblies/Sqlclr.Services.dll'</span>
<span class="k">WITH PERMISSION_SET</span> = <span class="k">SAFE</span>;
<span class="g">GO</span>

<span class="k">CREATE PROCEDURE</span> dbo.usp_ServiceBoundary
<span class="k">AS EXTERNAL NAME</span> [Sqlclr.Services].[Boundary].[Execute];
<span class="g">GO</span>  <span class="c">-- governed. verifiable. in-engine.</span></code></pre>
    </figure>
  </div>

  <a class="scroll-hint" href="#story" aria-label="Scroll to the story">
    <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
      <path d="m6 9 6 6 6-6" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
    </svg>
  </a>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    min-height: 100svh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding-block: clamp(7rem, 14vh, 10rem) 5rem;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .hero-bg { position: absolute; inset: 0; pointer-events: none; }
  .grid-lines {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(var(--line) 1px, transparent 1px),
      linear-gradient(90deg, var(--line) 1px, transparent 1px);
    background-size: 72px 72px;
    mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 70% at 50% 30%, black 20%, transparent 75%);
    -webkit-mask-image: radial-gradient(ellipse 90% 70% at 50% 30%, black 20%, transparent 75%);
    opacity: 0.55;
  }
  .glow {
    position: absolute;
    border-radius: 50%;
    filter: blur(90px);
  }
  .glow-1 {
    width: 640px; height: 640px;
    top: -220px; right: -140px;
    background: var(--glow-blue);
  }
  .glow-2 {
    width: 520px; height: 520px;
    bottom: -260px; left: -160px;
    background: var(--glow-ember);
  }

  .hero-inner { display: grid; gap: 1.9rem; position: relative; }
  /* grid items default to min-width:auto — the terminal's code line would stretch the track past the viewport on phones */
  .hero-inner > * { min-width: 0; }
  .hero-cta { display: flex; gap: 0.9rem; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-top: 0.4rem; }

  .terminal {
    margin-top: 2.6rem;
    max-width: 640px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    border: 1px solid var(--line-strong);
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, #0d1117, #0a0e14);
    box-shadow: 0 30px 80px -30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8), 0 0 0 1px rgba(88, 166, 255, 0.05);
  }
  .terminal-bar {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    padding: 0.7rem 1rem;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
  }
  .dot { width: 11px; height: 11px; border-radius: 50%; }
  .terminal-title {
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.72rem;
    color: var(--text-faint);
  }
  .terminal pre {
    padding: 1.2rem 1.35rem 1.35rem;
    overflow-x: auto;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.83rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: #c9d5e3;
  }
  .terminal .k { color: #79b8ff; font-weight: 500; }
  .terminal .s { color: #a5d6a7; }
  .terminal .c { color: #5c6a7d; font-style: italic; }
  .terminal .g { color: #f0a35c; }

  .scroll-hint {
    position: absolute;
    left: 50%;
    bottom: 1.8rem;
    transform: translateX(-50%);
    color: var(--text-faint);
    animation: bob 2.4s ease-in-out infinite;
  }
  @keyframes bob {
    0%, 100% { transform: translate(-50%, 0); }
    50% { transform: translate(-50%, 7px); }
  }
</style>
